    Does OPA figure it out on its own?
        Yes, OPA evaluates the package and rules corresponding to the specified data path. If no path is specified or matches, OPA cannot determine which policy to evaluate.

Best Practices for Managing Policies

    Clear Namespaces:
        Organize policies into meaningful packages (e.g., security.authentication, security.authorization).

